# Frontend Integration Rules

- Keep `apps/web` API clients aligned with backend envelope format.
- For lists (`orders`, `clients`) consume `{ data, meta }` and map both fields.
- For detail/create/update safely unwrap `res.data?.data ?? res.data`.
- Keep Vite shared-types alias pointing to ESM build:
  - `@lama-stage/shared-types` -> `packages/shared-types/dist/esm`
- After contract changes, verify pages:
  - `Klienci`
  - `Zlecenia`
  with no runtime import errors and no request `500`.
- Build produkcyjny serwowany przez nginx to **`apps/web/dist`** (por. reguła produkcyjna); smoke lokalny: `npm run smoke` / `API_URL` według potrzeb.

